    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/>DN IVSTINIANVS PP AVG (Obverse inscription)
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>Translation: Our Lord Justinian, Perpetual Augustus</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>This gold solidus was minted during the reign of Emperor Justinian I in Constantinople. It was discovered in Xi'an, China, and is evidence of trade routes connecting the Byzantine Empire with the Far East.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography">
